{"tid":2025371,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【知法犯法】巡視曾正科僭建　屋宇署遭驅趕恐嚇「放狗咬X你」","createTime":"2020-05-20T07:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T08:48:31.000Z","uid":6497,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9f020957443bc5a3c7bbe92203d98d9e8265ef","tid":2025371,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200520/XVJ2FWAUE55VWZMSQBR2H4GBDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FXVJ2FWAUE55VWZMSQBR2H4GBDA%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=0f08384e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FXVJ2FWAUE55VWZMSQBR2H4GBDA%2F&h=ec952cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200520/XVJ2FWAUE55VWZMSQBR2H4GBDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n新界北總區副指揮官曾正科在荃灣川龍持有的多幅土地及物業，被揭發疑霸佔官地及僭建。繼昨日地政署到場視察後，今再有屋宇署委聘的顧問公司人員到場視察僭建情況，惟其間有自稱村民人士驅趕顧問人員及記者，更恐嚇指「有村民打你唔關我事」、「村民放狗咬X你」，又指令涉事人員「叫屋宇署約時間去村公所傾」。"},{"pid":"f3cbdfd09a045fff0a6de2c17061a0e862f9385f","tid":2025371,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"caa68fd43a2898e9e4e4006c1da6933af89f3959","tid":2025371,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"真正狗屋"},{"pid":"b4447f3a2ef1d1d5f26357ef762b2152799771e6","tid":2025371,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"無法無天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d50a7074e5556c0f551fae57d31a01f6c8a729d","tid":2025371,"uid":238214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"刑事恐嚇？"},{"pid":"a24f36a69bc23e0a7dc100cb94e2c8f6ed0afd49","tid":2025371,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4447f3a2ef1d1d5f26357e